OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775052666
OL,3,CTrump says UK should 'build up delayed
OL,4,Ccourage' and secure Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FDonald Trump has told the UK and other
OL,7,Fallies to "build up some delayed
OL,8,Fcourage" and secure the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz as it remains largely closed
OL,10,Fdue to the ongoing war in Iran.
OL,12,FIn a Truth Social post on Tuesday, the
OL,13,FUS president said countries that
OL,14,F"refused to get involved in the
OL,15,Fdecapitation of Iran" should "build up
OL,16,Fsome delayed courage, go to the strait
OL,17,Fand just take it".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
