CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775052666
OL,3,CTrump says UK should 'build up delayed
OL,4,Ccourage' and secure Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FHe wrote: "All of those countries that
OL,7,Fcan't get jet fuel because of the
OL,8,FStrait of Hormuz, like the United
OL,9,FKingdom, which refused to get involved
OL,10,Fin the decapitation of Iran, I have a
OL,11,Fsuggestion for you: Number 1, buy from
OL,12,Fthe U.S., we have plenty, and Number
OL,13,F2, build up some delayed courage, go
OL,14,Fto the Strait, and just TAKE IT.
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775052666
OL,3,CTrump says UK should 'build up delayed
OL,4,Ccourage' and secure Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,F"You'll have to start learning how to
OL,7,Ffight for yourself, the U.S.A. won't
OL,8,Fbe there to help you anymore, just
OL,9,Flike you weren't there for us. Iran
OL,10,Fhas been, essentially, decimated. The
OL,11,Fhard part is done. Go get your own
OL,12,Foil!"
OL,14,FThe UK was the only country named in
OL,15,Fthe post.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775052666
OL,3,CTrump says UK should 'build up delayed
OL,4,Ccourage' and secure Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FHis comments come as he reportedly
OL,7,Ftold aides he would be willing to end
OL,8,Fthe war even if the Strait, an
OL,9,Fessential waterway through which a
OL,10,Ffifth of the world's oil passes,
OL,11,Fremains largely closed, the Wall
OL,12,FStreet Journal reported.
OL,14,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio
OL,15,Fappeared to contradict these claims in
OL,16,Fan interview with Al Jazeera, saying
OL,17,Fthat it will be kept open "one way or
OL,18,Fanother" and that US war objectives
OL,19,Fcould be achieved "in weeks, not
OL,20,Fmonths".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
