OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775052666
OL,3,CTrump says UK should 'build up delayed
OL,4,Ccourage' and secure Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FHe also insisted that communication
OL,7,Fbetween Tehran and Washington is
OL,8,Fongoing.
OL,10,FBut a spokesperson for Iran's Foreign
OL,11,FMinistry once again reiterated that no
OL,12,Fnegotiations had taken place, while
OL,13,Fconfirming that intermediaries had
OL,14,Fdelivered a set of proposals to Iran.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, US gas prices jumped past
OL,17,Fan average of $4 a gallon for the
OL,18,Ffirst time since 2022 on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
